quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  54,1,"The Hour has come near, and the moon has split [in two].{1}",footnotes:1:1
  54,2,"And if they see a sign [i.e., miracle], they turn away and say, "Passing magic."{1}",footnotes:1:1
  54,3,"And they denied and followed their inclinations. But for every matter is a [time of] settlement."
  54,4,"And there has already come to them of information that in which there is deterrence."
  54,5,"Extensive wisdom - but warning does not avail [them]."
  54,6,"So leave them, [O Muḥammad]. The Day the Caller{1} calls to something forbidding,",footnotes:1:1